Download sonarqube from offical website https://www.sonarsource.com/products/sonarqube/downloads/ in /opt directory

After downloading, navigate to /opt/sonarqube-10.6.0.92116/bin/linux-x86-64 and execute the following command to start/stop the sonarqube:
sh sonar.sh start/stop

Once sonarqube is running, access the sonarqube from browser with IP:9000
